<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0;" name="viewport" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>分享有礼</title>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://res.wx.qq.com/open/js/jweixin-1.3.2.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/fleiable.js"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px;
        }

        .bg {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
        }

        .first,
        .second,
        .third {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-con {
            width: calc(100% - 1rem);
            height: 100%;
            position: absolute;
            left: .5rem;
            background: #fff;
            top: 0px;
            left: .5rem;
            padding: .5rem 1rem;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .input-con .user-img {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .input-con .user-img img {
            width: 1.1rem;
            height: 1.1rem;
            background: red;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .input-con .user-name {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: .4rem;
            margin: .2rem 0;
        }
        .input-con .tips {
            color: #919191;
            font-size: .35rem;
            padding: 0rem .5rem;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: .45rem;
        }

        .rule-content {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0px;
            font-size: 0.31rem;
            color: #36383A;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            top: 1.6rem;
        }

        .rule-content .rule {
            line-height: .6rem;
            margin-top: .1rem;
        }
        .input-cell-single {
            border: 1px solid #F27169;
            border-radius: .1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: .2rem 0px;
            margin-top: .6rem;
        }
        .input-cell-single input {
            outline: none;
            width: calc(100% - .4rem);
            border: none;
            height: .8rem;
            margin-left: .2rem;
        }
        .input-cell {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border: 1px solid #F27169;
            border-radius: .1rem;
            margin-top: .5rem;
        }
        .input-cell input {
            outline: none;
            width: 50%;
            border: none;
            height: .8rem;
            margin-left: .2rem;
        }
        .input-cell input, .input-cell .btn-send {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .input-cell .btn-send {
            font-size: .35rem;
            text-align: center;
            background: #F45957;
            height: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.1rem;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .btn-get {
            padding: .35rem 0px;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: .35rem;
            background: linear-gradient(0deg,rgba(244,57,49,1),rgba(252,86,80,1));
            margin-top: 1.2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="first">
        <img class="bg" src="./img/get/img_new_red_envelopes_detailed_rules_of_the_activities.png">
    </div>
    <div class="second">
        <img class="bg" src="./img/code/img_new_red_envelopes_bg_2.png">
        <div class="input-con">
            <div class="user-img">
                <img src="">
            </div>
            <div class="user-name">
                土豆
            </div>
            <div class="tips">
                hi，送你一个超盟U品15元的红包哦，快来领取吧！
            </div>
            <div class="input-cell-single">
                <input type="text" placeholder="请输入手机号">
            </div>
            <div class="input-cell">
                <input type="text" placeholder="请输入验证码">
                <div class="btn-send">获取验证码</div>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-get">
                立即领取
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="third">
        <img class="bg" src="./img/code/img_new_red_envelopes_2.png">
        <div class="rule-content">
            <div class="rule">1.红包仅限超盟U品新用户领取</div>
            <div class="rule">2.同一手机号、同一微信号视为同一用户</div>
            <div class="rule">3.红包会在领取成功后48小时内发放入您的账号，您可在超盟U品小程序中查看</div>
            <div class="rule">4. 最终解释权，归超盟U品所有</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>